{"tid":175955,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金融時報：渣打CEO花紅要求降低　惹投資者不滿","createTime":"2017-03-28T00:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T01:01:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce71fab44bd89d2ef5f15531ce54dbdd533e374","tid":175955,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/081921_460e8b45029313584c53db65bd26c9ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F081921_460e8b45029313584c53db65bd26c9ce.jpg&h=237fa263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》報道，渣打集團（2888）及巴克萊銀行受到投資者批評，主要是由於這些銀行的行政總裁本身需要符合較高的業績表現，才可以獲取長期獎勵（Long-term Incentive Plan），但早前突然將業績目標大幅降低，令到高層容易拿取獎金。<br />\n<br />\n以渣打為例，本身行政總裁溫拓思（Bill Winters，圖）須要帶動銀行股本回報率（ROE）至到最少10%水平，但渣打決定減半，令到ROE只需要符合5%即可領取長期獎金。《金融時報》引述渣打集團頭15大投資者之一說：「銀行蝕緊錢，但高層仍然有錢收。」而一位頭20大投資者之一則說：「真係唔掂喎，咁都要畀Bonus佢？」<br />\n<br />\n該報引述渣打發言人回應指，該行去年在業績上有進展，但仍然需致力提高回報，而渣打薪酬委員會（降低達到長期獎勵門檻）目的是希望為該行提供更高回報。<br />\n<br />\n渣打去年ROE僅為0.3%，本身該行2018年目標為8%，2020年為10%，但去年已經放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56488867&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56488867%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170327&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=452e5242\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56488867%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170327&h=31d0608a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56488867&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170327</a>"},{"pid":"722f9028949e7cebbc33a9fdc57b5df192112482","tid":175955,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:22:09.000Z","msg":"降低目標攞獎金<im